\"M5 12.5l4.2 4.2L19 7\"/></svg></span> Unboxed &amp; snipped at 45°</div>\n      <div class=\"ck\"><span class=\"box empty\"></span> Hydrating in a cool, dark spot</div>\n      <div class=\"ck\"><span class=\"box empty\"></span> Workspace prepped with a tarp</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- testimonials -->\n<section class=\"calm\">\n  <div class=\"wrap\">\n    <div class=\"center\">\n      <div class=\"mono eyebrow\">EARLY REVIEWS</div>\n      <h2 class=\"lead center\">Brides &amp; testers are obsessed.</h2>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tcards\">\n      <figure class=\"tcard\">\n        <div class=\"stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <blockquote>\"It felt calm and not overwhelming. The pacing felt doable, and the encouraging notes along the way are such a great touch. It takes something most people find overwhelming and breaks it into sections with space to dream, organize, and plan.\"</blockquote>\n      </figure>\n      <figure class=\"tcard\">\n        <div class=\"stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <blockquote>\"The copy is so personable, it feels like a friend walking you through it. The checklists and tutorials are so easy to follow. If I were a bride, I would truly feel prepared to rock my own florals!\"</blockquote>\n      </figure>\n      <figure class=\"tcard\">\n        <div class=\"stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <blockquote>\"It thought of everything, the mood board, the budget estimator visuals, and being able to buy supplies right from the site. Such a time saver, and the tutorials are beautiful and easy to follow.\"</blockquote>\n      </figure>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:34px;\">\n      <a href=\"https://bloomculture.myflodesk.com/planner-preview\" class=\"btn btn-solid\">Try a free preview <span aria-hidden=\"true\">→</span></a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- pricing -->\n<section class=\"price\" id=\"get\">\n  <div class=\"wrap\">\n    <div class=\"center\">\n      <div class=\"mono eyebrow\" style=\"c