 or laptop, and your progress follows you across all of them.</p></details>\n      <details class=\"faq-item\"><summary><span class=\"spark\">❧</span> How long do I have it?</summary><p>Two full years from purchase, plenty of time for even the longest engagement. Revisit any module as many times as you need, right up to the big day.</p></details>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- closing -->\n<section class=\"closing\">\n  <div class=\"wrap\">\n    <img class=\"founder-photo\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0750/7984/4147/files/Alison_Fleck_Bloom_Culture_Founder.jpg?v=1780430641\" alt=\"Alison Fleck, founder of Bloom Culture\" />\n    <div class=\"founder-text\">\n      <div class=\"mono eyebrow\">A LITTLE NOTE FROM ALISON</div>\n      <p class=\"note\">\"After 20+ years in the floral world, I built this for the couple who wants to do their own flowers but has no idea where to begin, and could use some support. It doesn't have to be perfect to be beautiful, and you're so much more capable than you think.\"</p>\n      <p class=\"sig\">- Alison, founder of Bloom Culture</p>\n      <a href=\"https://bloomcultureflowers.com/products/diy-wedding-flower-planner\" class=\"btn btn-solid\">Start your flower plan, $49</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<footer>\n  <div class=\"name\">Bloom Culture<sup style=\"font-size:.5em;top:-.7em;\">TM</sup></div>\n  <div>DIY Wedding Flower Planner · Free with every flower order</div>\n</footer>\n\n\n<script>\n  function showBanner() {\n    var params = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);\n    if (params.get(\"status\") === \"unauthorized\") {\n      var banner = document.getElementById(\"bcf-alert-banner\");\n      if (banner) {\n        banner.style.display = \"block\";\n        banner.scrollIntoView({ behavior: \"smooth\" });\n      }\n    }\n  }\n  if (document.readyState === \"loading\") {\n    document.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", showBanner);\n  } else {\n    showBanner();\n  }\n</script>\n